data.description: Welcome to this stunning home that's been thoughtfully updated and meticulously maintained, offering an inviting and comfortable living experience. This residence boasts numerous recent upgrades, including a newer furnace and AC unit, ensuring year-round comfort and energy efficiency. Step inside and be greeted by the gleaming new flooring that flows seamlessly throughout the main living areas. The open floor plan provides a spacious and welcoming atmosphere, making it perfect for gatherings and everyday living. The basement offers an additional en suite. Outside, you'll find a beautiful oasis with an electric awning that offers shade and shelter, creating an ideal outdoor space for relaxation and entertainment. The community amenities are truly exceptional, offering a sparkling pool just a short walk away for those hot summer days, a serene community pond for tranquil walks, and a charming park for picnics and play. Whether you're enjoying the comforts of your updated home or taking advantage of the neighborhood amenities, this property offers the best of both worlds
